J Music[粵]
programme.desc: 嘉賓周吉佩率先偕主持冼靖峰柔聲對唱《假使世界原來不像你預期》，兩人對望一刻更有觸電感覺？吉吉亦透過新作《你是我唯一的》感謝身邊人，還帶來《梁山伯的華爾茲》，再背上結他自彈自唱《找自己》。另一嘉賓黃洛妍深情演繹《Dear Myself》，也跟與吉吉合唱英文歌，洛妍更因為吉吉而「臉紅紅」？此外，靖峰還會送上自家歌《BUG FIX》，並與洛妍互訴《日出時讓街燈安睡》。

programme.title: 晚間新聞[粵]
programme.desc: 報道本地、兩岸、國際重要新聞以及體育消息，讓你洞悉各地大事及體壇動向。

programme.title: 戀愛季節#5[粵]
programme.desc: 春芬演出生硬令拍攝無法順利進行，施辰向春芬表白，之後拍攝時兩人甚投入。麗花指施辰與春芬培養感情是為拍攝順利，春芬氣憤。宇軒與邱悠大吵時被狗仔隊拍到。天后廟將被拆卸，春芬遇祖安，指簽文說春芬緣份未盡。

programme.title: 東張西望[粵]
programme.desc: 年宵市場開鑼，乾貨及快餐熟食攤位自疫情後首次重臨維園，攝製隊入場視察，還會前往花墟一探銷情。某公司CEO早前企圖跳橋輕生獲途人勸阻，背後有何隱情？事主控訴代老闆墊支款項後，對方「唔認數」，無奈欠下債務……《東張西望》於台慶頒獎禮奪得「專業精神獎」，團隊聚餐慶功，並開心玩抽獎。《愛．回家之開心速遞》演員們出席深圳見面會，跟粉絲熱鬧互動。廉政公署為慶祝成立五十周年舉行跑步活動，影星甄子丹亦現身支持。

programme.title: Sunday好戲王[粵]
programme.desc: 重量級評判楊盼盼為車婉婉、胡鴻鈞、李璧琦、趙永洪的演技評定高下。「睇你點死」，四名參賽嘉賓扮演武林中人，死亡經歷有多離奇、搞笑？四人又於「我係大話精」自稱運動高手，分別擅長籃球、高爾夫球、乒乓球及羽毛球項目，還曾在公開賽得獎。各自「露兩手」，「必殺技」姿勢似模似樣，盼盼姐能否拆穿其中三位的「西洋鏡」？慈母形象深入民心的資深演員亮相「另類好戲王」，還分享盼望演繹的角色。

programme.title: 肥媽新年新煮意[粵]
programme.desc: 肥媽特地飛去馬來西亞教觀眾煮賀年菜，讓大家在新年可以自己煮出一道又一道特別又有創意的賀年菜。來到大馬，肥媽亦邀請了當地藝人當嘉賓，如:王翠玲、張棟樑等。

programme.title: 大灣區 活好D[粵]
programme.desc: 鄧以婷和區永權透過五感享受東莞之旅！到訪香薰工房親手做香薰石膏，調配自己的味道；特色素食餐館品嚐香味濃烈的榴槤披薩，精采的嗅覺味覺饗宴；搞怪甜品店狗仔甜品幾可亂真，帶來視覺味覺新衝擊。東莞新地標的大型商場，有「莞邑故事」主題街區，購物打卡一take過。到厚街尋覓東莞味覺歷史，食盡三間不同的燒鵝髀瀨粉，哪一間最掂？度假酒店主打池畔房間，隨時享受碧波蕩漾。多種特色溫泉，還有豐富自助餐，感觀大滿足。

programme.title: 兄弟姊妹去旅行[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 來到琉森湖旁的小鎮布龍嫩，子羚、定欣忽發奇想，要兩男跟瑞士人學唱歌，自己學吹阿爾卑斯長號及揮旗，還組成合唱團在湖邊開騷。兩位前歌手走音不斷，阿廉竟然「賴」瑞士空氣太好？兩男到軍刀專門店自製萬用軍刀，最終刻上誰的名字？四人坐船遊琉森湖，欣賞周邊景色及日落，順道交心，拋出一堆假設性問題，哪位看似較開放或花弗？走入一間花園式佈置的餐廳，享用「廚師發辦」餐，分享旅行的「怪異」經歷，阿廉有個真人真事要分享！

programme.title: 甜心先生[粵]
programme.desc: Regen (張惠雅)小學時已立志開甜品店，古嘉俊(阿古)在節目內與她分享做甜品心得，助她完成創業夢想。這次示範的「斑蘭芒果慕絲蛋糕」，材料與楊枝金露類同，當中還加入清香的斑蘭葉油，口味絕不平凡。為了做出別緻賣相，阿古先後用上各式工具，Regen把握機會向阿古請教甜品製作秘訣，結果得知多項「商業秘密」。甜品師如何讓客人隨時品嚐到四季時令口味？阿古做甜品時，為何以急凍雞蛋取代新鮮雞蛋？

programme.title: 食平3D[粵]
programme.desc: 近年的番薯竟然種出雪糕味，「一個人的晚餐」肥媽用雪糕味番薯做出番薯味雪糕！肥媽一次忘記煮晚飯，錯有錯着下發明了「雙響牛角酥」，有何厲害之處？至於「燒雞胸配甜椒茴香沙律」，適合喜歡清淡的朋友享用。

programme.title: 食平3D[粵]
programme.desc: 肥媽煮排骨確有一手，「陳皮骨」有何秘訣？黑蒜近年成為養生食物新寵，生吃口感微酸且甜，加入蜜豆炒帶子最適合。學習「粟米牛奶濃湯」製法外，且看六號示範「極速粟米起粒法」。肥媽還炮製甜品「黃糖肉桂蝴蝶酥」。

programme.title: 阿爺廚房[粵]
programme.desc: 鼎爺、阿譚在順德隨師傅手製龍江煎堆，炸煎堆切勿貪快。而製作巨型煎堆的關鍵食材，在於特製的爆谷和老糖水？再往陳村品嚐時令花宴，單是賣相已無比吸睛。主持們烹調賀年「吉祥元寶湯」，以蛋角取其元寶意頭，包元寶有何技巧？注意熬湯時加入食材的次序，避免影響湯水味道。再來一道「鴻運片皮雞」，處理片皮雞甚考功夫，先用五香水淋上雞隻，再吊起風乾，怎樣令雞皮達致香脆效果？配上沙葛、饅頭品嚐，可中和片皮雞的油膩感。

programme.title: 阿爺廚房[粵]
programme.desc: 農曆新年將至，鼎爺炮製矜貴「阿爺佛跳牆」，材料有鮑魚、珧柱、鹿腳筋、海參、花膠、雞等，還採用雞腳、瘦肉熬湯底！處理鹿腳筋步驟較繁複，留意鼎爺指導如何將腳筋弄至軟身，還要注意材料的燉煮次序。鼎爺和阿譚到澳門，品嚐融合葡國菜和中國菜特色的美食，當中亦有一道「佛跳牆」，有何特色？鼎爺再整金黃香脆「賀年油角」，搓好麵糰後謹記預留鬆筋時間。至於製作賀年「陳皮紅豆糕」時，怎樣令紅豆粒粒分明且分布平均？

programme.desc: 酵素可以內服外用，替我們的身體和肌膚做「環保」。美容達人袁觀玲介紹含有酵素的洗顏品和護膚品，又分享日本超人氣的酵素飲食；「愛美麗盲測」評比四款在台灣發售的酵素洗顏粉，比較各產品的優勝之處。現代人生活忙碌，日常飲食難以攝取到足夠的營養，「愛美麗時尚」走訪台北市政府捷運站旁的一間食店，店子以心智飲食及生酮飲食為概念，供應防彈咖啡、色彩繽紛的蔬果汁，以及多種低卡全素無麩質蛋糕。

programme.title: 就是愛美麗[粵/普]
programme.desc: 髮界達人吳依霖示範2019流行編髮，又教大家利用髮飾，打造出氣質、日系、韓系等不同造型風格的髮型。想髮型好看，除了練習綁髮的技巧，「愛美麗時尚」還到訪台北擁有超過30年歷史的假髮專門店，讓大家為髮型設計找出新的加分效果。不少人有髮線後移的煩惱，「愛美麗盲測」測試四款來自台灣、韓國及日本的增髮產品的自然度、防水度及均勻度，評比哪種才是「增髮神器」。

programme.title: 姊妹淘[粵]
programme.desc: 除了愛情之外，親情和友情也相當珍貴，遇上幾個投契的知己或與兄弟姊妹關係良好，實在是人生一大美事。正如今集的嘉賓AOA是一對孿生姊妹花，二人感情非常要好，現在更連工作及休息時間都在一起，彼此也缺少不了對方。有不少人說孿生姐妹有著神奇的心靈感應，到底二人是否真的有這種能力呢？另外，節目請來了塔羅師Jan Jan，她帶同了一部可以測試氣場的儀器到來。這個機器可以幫助大家知道自己發出的能量氣場，從中得知自己的身心靈狀況，更可了解自己的性格，AOA與主持們都紛紛搶著試玩。

programme.title: 開端#11[粵/普]

programme.title: 鄉下走一回[粵/韓]

programme.title: MUSIC BREAK[粵]
programme.desc: 本集由李茵彤Desta(@desta_l_e_e)推介歌單，播放的MV包括「勁歌推介」薛家燕、茜拉Shila《有有有Year of the Yo!》；張敬軒《青春告別式》、陳健安《繼續繼續》、MC張天賦《救命稻草》、小塵埃《拼命優雅》、Mike曾比特《魔氈》。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 本應是愉快的韓國之旅，期間一次意外卻令歌手迪子跌進人生低谷。迪子在咖啡店內絆倒，面部撞向鋼椅，導致牙齒、嘴部嚴重受創，出事後更要大幅度縫針。除了親述這段觸目驚心的受傷經過，迪子又提到當時囑咐朋友為她隱瞞家人，何以有此想法？迪子性格樂觀，還拿嘴部的傷口自嘲，笑言化身日漫角色！她亦不忘拍照紀錄傷勢，但起初原因竟是為了求救？迪子及後進行牙齒修復之外，也要接受整容療程，且聽她細訴臉上部位的調整情況。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 意外帶來的不一定只有負面挫折，女歌手迪子受傷破相，經歷反讓她較前更有自信。她還將箇中體會融入音樂作品，唱出普遍人口說不介意別人外貌，實際卻是另一回事。迪子意外後要接受整容治療，更自拍歷程製作MV。手術醒來一刻，竟還不忘拍攝！她亦揭開整容的神秘一面，例如手術後要坐着睡覺的原因。歌曲以綑綁帶出愛情關係，迪子又認為每段戀愛總有「S」與「M」，何出此言？她數年前毅然與唱片公司「分手」，又是為了甚麼緣故？

programme.title: 北歐潮什麼[粵]
programme.desc: 挪威最大的海盜主題樂園，廣受大、小朋友喜愛。芷珮攜眷入場，勇闖迷宮、試玩掘金，還登上海盜船，體驗海上激戰！一家人樂而忘返，索性住進海盜主題酒店，全情投入海盜世界。芷珮及後慕名到訪世界級咖啡店，一試冠軍咖啡師的手藝。西南部城市斯塔萬格，開設了十多個特色博物館。罐頭博物館兼工場，可認識製作沙甸魚罐頭的步驟，並一嚐以傳統方法燻燒的沙甸魚。石油博物館則展示探挖、生產石油的歷史，芷珮了解後更揚言要轉行鑽油！

programme.title: 還原神之食[粵]
programme.desc: 這集繼續力求還原《美味天王》菜式，並參考劇中古天樂製作的「石燒芝士龍蝦」，積奇更指菜餚跟法式名菜「龍蝦米多」相似。欣茵、泳芍仿照劇集情節，做菜前先挑選龍蝦。海鮮達人為她們準備了朱龍、澳洲岩龍、法國藍龍等，並分享揀龍蝦要訣。古天樂於劇內教導徒弟揀選「孖指」龍蝦，原來這確是要領之一？積奇把龍蝦起肉走油，加入法式白醬、芝士烹調，然後放回龍蝦殼入爐焗香。期間欣茵要求加進伊麵，卻被積奇取笑她令菜式降格。

programme.title: 古靈精怪 台灣篇[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 暉哥手臂上的傷口好逼真，似足被喪屍咬過，可惜演技未到家，被婭彤、茜佳輕易拆穿！三人向電影特效化妝師學藝，「斷手指」的婭彤更稱感覺到痛楚？有神明可讓善信祈求變靚？貪靚主持們帶同私伙化妝品，到訪清朝古廟拜「醫美之神」。特色園區集文物館、廟宇於一身，古今中外雕塑、文物珍藏令人大開眼界！泰國四面佛藏身停車場旁一個只有電梯般大小的空間，佛像還會「自轉」！橋底的推車式廟宇亦甚獨特，所供奉的原來是「落難神明」。

programme.desc: Christy、Jessica往潮人集中地肯頓巿集，體驗潮流文化和美食！45cm巨型牛角包，捧著點浸咖啡打卡才是重點！液氮雪糕新鮮「冒烟」即製，更有英式甜品口味。以「糖果屋」童話為主題的甜品店，以棉花糖盛載雪糕，夠夢幻！結合音樂、舞蹈、派對等元素的Cyber服裝店是朝聖必選，換上前衛閃爍螢光時裝，仿如置身狂野派對、虛擬空間！兩位主持又跟導師學做傳統「維多利亞海綿蛋糕」，Christy不忘盡情偷師！

programme.desc: Christy、Jessica穿上型格「牛仔」便服，尋找隱世名店盡情打卡！古老建築內原是網紅餐廳，共設五個不同風格的用餐區，其中以粉紅色為主調的茶館供食客享用甜品，感覺超夢幻！蘇豪區黃金地段隱藏「人氣」蛋糕店，賣相吸引的紙杯蛋糕大受歡迎，老闆娘「爆紅」原來有段勵志故事？醋廠跳蚤市場可找到不少特色古著，Veronica遇上想法一致的檔主，可有收獲？兩位主持再去紅磚巷市集「掃街」，感受地道文化氣息！

programme.title: 不如食豪D[粵]
programme.desc: Gin Lee愛吃日式火鍋，尚友專誠用貴價海螯蝦製作火鍋料理。藝人常要戒口，Gin卻稱打邊爐「凍食」就無問題？她自揭馬來西亞家園種植菠蘿、蔗等，6號驚訝空間限制想像！以貓屎咖啡做提拉米蘇，滋味昇華。為測Gin打發忌廉功力，搞鬼6號在她頭上倒轉忌廉碗……撒朱古力粉時，她勾起童年回憶，還笑言曾「運粉」來港。該飲品港版、大馬版試味挑戰，她竟飲到發脾氣？回望在港發展辛酸，她為慳錢不出街，更差點放棄歌手夢？

programme.title: 開卷[粵]
programme.desc: 主持們這次到訪的書店位於基隆港附近，店內很多東西都含有海洋的元素，樓上還提供享用咖啡與休憩的空間，韻婷更即席玩手鼓自娛！書店老闆在海邊居住，曾從事跟海洋有關的工作，由他推介的讀物有何特別？自由潛愛好者泳芍揀來以「幻想」視角窺探深海之書，卻發覺自己對海洋的熟知度不足！由日本心理學家撰寫的書籍，採用漫畫形式將職場的心理學表達出來。隨着故事發展，讀者還可學習怎樣於初見面予人良好印象，甚或一些戀愛技巧。

programme.desc: 挪威最大的海盜主題樂園，廣受大、小朋友喜愛。芷珮攜眷入場，勇闖迷宮、試玩掘金，還登上海盜船，體驗海上激戰！一家人樂而忘返，索性住進海盜主題酒店，全情投入海盜世界。芷珮及後慕名到訪世界級咖啡店，一試冠軍咖啡師的手藝。西南部城市斯塔萬格，開設了十多個特色博物館。罐頭博物館兼工場，可認識製作沙甸魚罐頭的步驟，並一嚐以傳統方法燻燒的沙甸魚。石油博物館則展示探挖、生產石油的歷史，芷珮了解後更揚言要轉行鑽油！

programme.title: 還原神之食[粵]
programme.desc: 這集繼續力求還原《美味天王》菜式，並參考劇中古天樂製作的「石燒芝士龍蝦」，積奇更指菜餚跟法式名菜「龍蝦米多」相似。欣茵、泳芍仿照劇集情節，做菜前先挑選龍蝦。海鮮達人為她們準備了朱龍、澳洲岩龍、法國藍龍等，並分享揀龍蝦要訣。古天樂於劇內教導徒弟揀選「孖指」龍蝦，原來這確是要領之一？積奇把龍蝦起肉走油，加入法式白醬、芝士烹調，然後放回龍蝦殼入爐焗香。期間欣茵要求加進伊麵，卻被積奇取笑她令菜式降格。

programme.title: 黃金庭院#27[粵/韓]
programme.desc: 東珠要Sabrina歸還用東珠身分搶走的一切，蘭淑阻止。東珠找到身世知道蘭淑非生母，找律師提出訴訟拿回一切。東珠與蘭淑深談不歡而散，Sabrina求東珠別將往事告訴南熙。奶奶和秀美得知部分MS病友的股份被同一人買下。

programme.title: 網紅甜卡[粵]
programme.desc: Christy、Jessica穿上型格「牛仔」便服，尋找隱世名店盡情打卡！古老建築內原是網紅餐廳，共設五個不同風格的用餐區，其中以粉紅色為主調的茶館供食客享用甜品，感覺超夢幻！蘇豪區黃金地段隱藏「人氣」蛋糕店，賣相吸引的紙杯蛋糕大受歡迎，老闆娘「爆紅」原來有段勵志故事？醋廠跳蚤市場可找到不少特色古著，Veronica遇上想法一致的檔主，可有收獲？兩位主持再去紅磚巷市集「掃街」，感受地道文化氣息！

programme.title: 不如食豪D[粵]
programme.desc: Gin Lee愛吃日式火鍋，尚友專誠用貴價海螯蝦製作火鍋料理。藝人常要戒口，Gin卻稱打邊爐「凍食」就無問題？她自揭馬來西亞家園種植菠蘿、蔗等，6號驚訝空間限制想像！以貓屎咖啡做提拉米蘇，滋味昇華。為測Gin打發忌廉功力，搞鬼6號在她頭上倒轉忌廉碗……撒朱古力粉時，她勾起童年回憶，還笑言曾「運粉」來港。該飲品港版、大馬版試味挑戰，她竟飲到發脾氣？回望在港發展辛酸，她為慳錢不出街，更差點放棄歌手夢？

programme.title: 開卷[粵]
programme.desc: 主持們這次到訪的書店位於基隆港附近，店內很多東西都含有海洋的元素，樓上還提供享用咖啡與休憩的空間，韻婷更即席玩手鼓自娛！書店老闆在海邊居住，曾從事跟海洋有關的工作，由他推介的讀物有何特別？自由潛愛好者泳芍揀來以「幻想」視角窺探深海之書，卻發覺自己對海洋的熟知度不足！由日本心理學家撰寫的書籍，採用漫畫形式將職場的心理學表達出來。隨着故事發展，讀者還可學習怎樣於初見面予人良好印象，甚或一些戀愛技巧。

programme.title: 紅色高踭鞋#11[粵/韓][PG]
programme.desc: 故事講述一名背叛了丈夫和生病的兒子，為了愛情和慾望拋家棄子的母親，與懷著對母親怨恨的女兒多年後再次見面，並開始對自己母親展開復仇計畫。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 本應是愉快的韓國之旅，期間一次意外卻令歌手迪子跌進人生低谷。迪子在咖啡店內絆倒，面部撞向鋼椅，導致牙齒、嘴部嚴重受創，出事後更要大幅度縫針。除了親述這段觸目驚心的受傷經過，迪子又提到當時囑咐朋友為她隱瞞家人，何以有此想法？迪子性格樂觀，還拿嘴部的傷口自嘲，笑言化身日漫角色！她亦不忘拍照紀錄傷勢，但起初原因竟是為了求救？迪子及後進行牙齒修復之外，也要接受整容療程，且聽她細訴臉上部位的調整情況。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 意外帶來的不一定只有負面挫折，女歌手迪子受傷破相，經歷反讓她較前更有自信。她還將箇中體會融入音樂作品，唱出普遍人口說不介意別人外貌，實際卻是另一回事。迪子意外後要接受整容治療，更自拍歷程製作MV。手術醒來一刻，竟還不忘拍攝！她亦揭開整容的神秘一面，例如手術後要坐着睡覺的原因。歌曲以綑綁帶出愛情關係，迪子又認為每段戀愛總有「S」與「M」，何出此言？她數年前毅然與唱片公司「分手」，又是為了甚麼緣故？

programme.title: Health - I Want Peace & Quiet
programme.desc: The people of Donbass have faced profound psychological traumas, and are now grappling with the torment of the aftermath. Psychologists from the People's Front arrived in Severodonetsk to help ease the process of recovery for them. Discover the techniques they use and find out whether overcoming PTSD is really possible.

programme.title: History - Remembrance
programme.desc: When Auschwitz was freed on January 27, 1945, the survivors met their liberators with shouts of “the Russians have come.” Some 70 years later, the Red Army’s instrumental role in defeating the Nazis in WWII is being wiped from Western history books. However, not all have forgotten who stopped Hitler’s war machine. Those who remember still honour their tremendous sacrifices.

programme.title: Sport - Knockout Girls
programme.desc: To them, boxing is more than just a sport: it gives freedom, empowerment and the confidence to stand up for themselves. They're the students of Karachi’s first boxing school for girls. Training here, they feel better able to protect themselves but more than that, they also know they achieve more than what their conservative society expects of them.

programme.title: Military and War - Donbass: Echoes of War
programme.desc: The history of Donbass is deeply linked to World War II; the intense battles fought there and the heroism shown by the people continue to shape the region's identity and resilience to this day. Today, in the same locales where Donbass defenders fought against Hitler, their descendants continue the legacy, fighting against Ukrainian nationalists. Explore the chronicles of WWII's heaviest battles and delve into the stories of Donbass heroes, both from the past and the present.

programme.title: Health - Last Wishes
programme.desc: This is a game in which the stake is human life. These people play with death. While the grim reaper stands at the head of the dying person’s bed, waiting for their final breath, volunteers from the Dutch “Ambulance Wish Foundation” arrive. They are prepared to fulfil any last wish of the patient. Completely free of charge!

programme.title: Newborn Russia - Urgent C-section to save the lives of mother and child - Newborn Russia (E24)
programme.desc: Oksana is expecting her first child with her husband Maksim. They’ve been together since their late teens. Sudden complications left her doctors with no choice but to prepare an urgent C-section. In the operating theatre every second counts as Oksana’s condition could kill both her and the baby.

programme.title: Newborn Russia - It Doesn’t Have To Be Painful - Newborn Russia (E25)
programme.desc: Elena is a doctor and with her husband, Anton, is expecting a second daughter. She obeyed the rules all through her pregnancy and has a textbook C-section. Her name-sake though drank and smoked in early pregnancy and now has complications. Issues with her blood mean the second Elena is transferred to a specialist unit where she suffers intense labour pains before giving birth to a boy.

programme.title: Newborn Russia - Twin Surprise & a family of high flyers - Newborn Russia (E26)
programme.desc: Kristina and her husband Andrey work as flight attendants. Kristina is about to give birth to their baby, and she wants Andrey to be by her side. He finds this much more frightening than flying over the ocean. He feels sure he’ll faint, but decides it’s his duty to support his wife. Meanwhile, the doctors are making bets on whether or not he’ll manage.

programme.title: Newborn Russia - Older Mothers - Newborn Russia (E27)
programme.desc: Giving birth later in life can bring complications. It’s fifteen years since Elena, 40, had her first child and she’s facing risks. Sudden pains lead to a tricky emergency C-section to bring her son into the world. Maria is philosophical about giving birth and tries to enjoy the moment with her husband Andrey. In the end, her c-section is faultless and she says hello to baby Alisa.

programme.title: Newborn Russia - Mother Love - Newborn Russia (E28)
programme.desc: Natalya’s parents don’t approve of her marriage and aren’t there to support her when she has her third child, Ilya. It’s the complete opposite for Marina whose husband is away working, so mother Irina is on hand. As well as giving moral support throughout the birth, Irina’s job is to video the event for all the family to see.

programme.title: Newborn Russia - Coming To Term - Newborn Russia (E29)
programme.desc: Evgenia is having her third child, and at the age of 31, the doctors say it won’t be easy. The longer she has to wait, the riskier it becomes so labour has to be induced. Eventually, Evgenia gives birth to little Alyona. Also on the ward is Inna whose first child is much easier as the delivery goes without a hitch and husband, Dmitry looks on as she gives birth to a girl.

programme.title: Investigation - Ukraine: Drug Testing Ground
programme.desc: Oleg Suprun was in charge of the town hospital in Donbass when it was seized by Ukrainian nationalists in 2014. The man was struck by their level of cruelty. Eventually, Oleg discovered that Ukrainian troops used potent psychotropic drugs. ‘More than once, I saw syringes in their pockets with butorphanol’, Oleg recalls. These drugs are believed to suppress the fear of death and greatly increase endurance, but at what cost?

programme.title: Lifestyle - Philadelphia - Addicted to Freedom
programme.desc: In 2023, homelessness surged again in Philadelphia, marking a three- year increase, as per the annual survey. Homelessness affects people from all walks of life, stripping them of dignity and safety. Many turn to crime out of desperation. Entire neighbourhoods are deserted, while the homeless blatantly inject drugs in broad daylight on trash-ridden streets.

programme.title: Environment - Protect Oak Flat
programme.desc: Oak Flat is a unique area that is considered sacred to the indigenous Apache people. For thousands of years, Oak Flat was a place for spiritual ceremonies and prayer. They believe it’s home to deities, medicinal plants and healing spring waters. However, Oak Flat has been under threat of destruction since 2014 when Congress passed legislation that allows transferring the holy site to the foreign mining giant, Resolution Copper, which wants to extract one of the largest untapped copper reserves in North America. The documentary tells the stories of Native American activists and environmentalists fighting against mining at Oak Flat.

programme.title: Environment - Diving for Gold
programme.desc: Residents of Pinut-an barangay in the Philippines know their way around gold. Why do they survive on rice and water? The truth is, they are gold divers, and their job is to collect gold nuggets from the bottom of the ocean. The mining is hazardous and even illegal, yet they have no other choice. How come people surrounded by gold are doomed to live in poverty?

programme.title: Military and War - Middle East: Vicious Circle of Violence
programme.desc: In our new documentary delving into the historical roots of the Israel-Palestine conflict and the poignant stories from both sides, examine the ongoing crisis in the Middle East. What sparked the Hamas movement? How did they succeed in attacking the Gaza Strip, despite being closely watched by Israeli satellites? What are those factors triggering the endless cycle of violence and prolonged war?

programme.title: Society - Russophobia
programme.desc: Shortly after Russia's military operation in Ukraine began, many Russians abroad felt a surge of Russophobia from mainstream media and some Western politicians, to everyday interactions. Russians are losing their jobs and even being threatened with violence. How are they coping with the abuse?

programme.title: Health - Abortion: America’s Divide
programme.desc: On 19 May 2021, the Republican Governor of Texas, Greg Abbott, signed one of the strictest and most scandalous abortion laws in the US, the Heartbeat Act. It prohibits abortion from the sixth week of pregnancy. Such a controversial decision sparked a wave of public unrest among pro-choicers supported by celebs like Uma Thurman and Lady Gaga. However, this outrage was not unanimous. Some women have other points of view. So what do both sides have to say?

programme.title: History - Remembrance

programme.title: Human Rights - The Afghan Woman King
programme.desc: "The Afghan Woman King" is a story of an unusual Pashtun woman from the province of Khost on the border between Afghanistan and Pakistan. Bibi Hokmeena looks like a middle-aged man, clad in pants and a vest and wearing a traditional turban instead of a paranja. She carries a gun and a dagger and is not afraid to use them. She's braver than many men and is not afraid to speak out opposing injustice against women.

programme.title: The Silk Road Series - Tourism on the Silk Road
programme.desc: As China is setting a course to revive the Silk Road with its ‘One Belt, One Road’ initiative, we visit the key cities on the renowned ancient trade route. Learn the story behind the discovery of the famous terracotta army in Xi’an, visit Lanzhou for a traditional tea ceremony, and find out what ailments are treated with acupuncture in Ürümqi.

programme.title: Military and War - Leningrad Unbreakable
programme.desc: The documentary commemorates 80 years since the liberation of Leningrad from the Nazi blockade. It showcases the unwavering resilience of Leningraders, who, despite hunger and constant shelling, donated 144 tons of blood over the years, to aid injured soldiers on the front lines. Also, they never ceased the production of guns needed by the Soviet Army to fight against the Nazis.

programme.title: Travel and Adventure - Hot Race, Cold Dogs
programme.desc: 2,100 kilometres across Kamchatka’s vast, snowy wilderness in a month! It’s the annual Beringia dog sled race that pits 15 teams against each other on grueling terrain in subzero temperatures and ferocious winds. The mushers and dogs are nevertheless ready to face off and fight for a prize of nearly $50,000. Ready, steady, mush mush!

programme.title: Lifestyle - Wi-Fi Refugees
programme.desc: They are forced out of society into involuntary seclusion, away from civilisation. Their tormentor is invisible – and it’s gaining power and expanding its reach day by day. However, most people consider it to be harmless, and look upon those claiming otherwise with distrust. The victims are called electrosensitive people, and they are running out of places where they can hide from the waves produced by wireless and cell phone technology.
